title: Cornelia Street
description:
There's been a lot of speculation but we know exactly what, or rather WHO, Taylor Swift is singing about in this song! Find out who made Cornelia Street so important, and why we know without a doubt who this song is about. You just have to listen to what Taylor really says!
What did we miss? What else would you like to hear? There are many ways to get in touch with us!
